1. Ingress Types
  --> Ingress backed by a single Service (All requests to single backend service)
      --> Single Backend service
      --> Default Backend
  --> Simple fanout (Path based routing)
  --> Name based virtual hosting (hostname based routing)
  
2. Types of Routing
  Path based routing : http://example.com/wear, http://example.com/video
  Host based routing : http://wear.example.com, http://video.example.com
 
